rComments: This professor is funny even when he doesn't mean to be funny. His best trait is teaching material and then giving you homework that actually corresponds to what he actually taught. It can get confusing sometimes because sometimes you don't know what the terms mean; but at least you know how to reliably get to the result.
Good class.  In my opinion he does explains topics clearly and is a fair grader.  Some students felt the class was to hard, but hey if you don't know what a mean, mode and median not blame him.
Can there be a worse teacher?
OMG - just get out while you can. Incomprehensible and totally maniacal attitude.
If you can avoid him, great, if not, you are fried.
